query:
SELECT
            kp.owner_did as did,
            encode(kp.key_package, 'base64') as key_package,
            kp.key_package_hash,
            kp.cipher_suite
        FROM key_packages kp
        WHERE kp.owner_did = $1
          AND kp.device_id = $2
          AND kp.consumed_at IS NULL
          AND kp.expires_at > $3
          AND (kp.reserved_at IS NULL OR kp.reserved_at < $4)
        ORDER BY kp.created_at ASC
        LIMIT 1
